          "block_order": 2
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "None of my friends came to see me that day.那天没有一朋看我9.疑问代词：用来提出问题的代词称为疑问代词。\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            69,
            722,
            2017,
            908
          ],
          "block_id": 3,
          "block_order": 3
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "(1) who、whom.whose、what.which.whoever、whatever、whichever主要用\n特殊疑问句中，一般放在句首。口语中也常用who代替whom作宾语，但\n在介词后则只能用whom.\n\n如：whom did you invite to your birthay party?\n(你都邀请了谁参加你的生日聚会的?)\n\nWhat does she want to be when she grows up?\n(她长大了想干什么？)\n\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            70,
            917,
            2025,
            1608
          ],
          "block_id": 4,
          "block_order": 4
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "(2) who和whom只能独立使用，其中who可以做句子的主语，表语或动词的宾语，whom只能作谓语动词的宾语；而what、which，whose等既可以独立使用作主语、表语和宾语，也可以与名词构成疑问短语。",
          "block_bbox": [
            65,
            1622,
            2027,
            1913
          ],
          "block_id": 5,
          "block_order": 5
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "如：who is thaot man? (那男的是谁?)\nWhat colour are their hats？ (他们的帽子是什么颜色?)Which car was made in Germany?(哪辆车是德国造的?)(被动)注意这个提问：The man in the car is my father.(车里的男人是我父亲\n→Which man is your father?(哪个男人是你的父亲?)",
          "block_bbox": [
            100,
            1938,
            2064,
            2439
          ],
          "block_id": 6,
          "block_order": 6
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "(3) which除了可以询问指代的情况之外，还可以针对说明人物的时间、地点、岁数、颜色、大小、状况等进行提问.2如：People there live a very sad life.(那里的人生活凄惨.)→Which people live a sad life?(哪些人生活凄惨？)",
          "block_bbox": [
            65,
            2450,
            2053,
            2862
          ],
          "block_id": 7,
          "block_order": 7
        },
        {
